Need to relax after the holidays? Come in and try our Marma Facial Massage. A good massage will leave you feeling refreshed and rejuvenated, the perfect way to start the new year. 

Marma is based on Ayurveda, a holistic, healthy lifestyle system of prevention and treatments used in India for over 5000 years. Some of the benefits: promotes healthy, glowing skin, reduces eye strain, increases your general immunity, increases total body circulation, and so much more! 

Call or stop by any of our four Bombay Brow locations; we would love to pamper you with our Marma Facial Massage.
